1.3.1	First , make sure your two computers are in the same workgroup : In ME , right click on 'Network Neighborhood ' and select 'Identification ' .	St
1.3.2	In XP , right click on 'My Computer ' and selct 'Properties ' .	St
1.3.3	Choose the 'Computer Name ' tab and click on 'Change ' .	St
1.3.4	Next , on your ME computer , turn on File sharing .	St
1.3.5	Get there by opening 'Network ' in the Control Panel .	St
1.3.6	Finally , choose the folder ( s ) you would like to share : Open 'Windows Explorer ' ( Windows Key + E ) .	St
1.3.7	Right click on the folder to be shared .	St
1.3.8	Choose 'Sharing ... ' Turn on sharing in the window that opens , and your done !	St
